      returned_data.push({name:item.product_name_ar,price:item.price.toFixed(2),category:item.subtitle,brand:item.title,last_scan:item.last_scan_time})
    ))
    await this.setState({
      rowData:returned_data
    })
    console.log('done');
  }
  render() {
    return (
      <div>
        <div style={{height:110,backgroundColor:'#6EB536',justifyContent: 'space-between',paddingHorizontal: 20,flexDirection: 'row',padding: 10,marginBottom: 10}}>
          <img src='./logo.png' alt="Logo" style={{width: 60}}/>
        </div>
        <div className="container">
          <div
          className="ag-theme-balham"
          style={{
            width:'100%',
            height:600
          }}
          >
            <AgGridReact
            columnDefs={this.state.columnDefs}
            rowData={this.state.rowData}
            headerHeight={80}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    );
  }

}
export default App;
